Assigns a user as support
show stats -> {show clients and supports, chat info, messages info}
getById and blah blah

support
First, the support admin has to assign it.
request is sent to the user (Do you agree to become support?) inline btn
if(reject) -> skip (does not change user)

if(accept) -> (Choose the languages you know) inline btn -> save changes ->
           -> contact with clients and sittings keyboard btn
           if(contact with clients) -> get client_ids ORDER BY created_at(Chat.Status.PENDING) DESC limit 1 ->
           -> pausa chat and end chat keyboard btn
                     if(pausa chat) -> ChatStatus.PAUSA
                     if(end chat) ->  ChatStatus.CLOSED save chat info and messages
                  if(sittings) -> change lang

